# Premium UI Components & Motion

**Part of Premium UI Standards** (Split 3 of 4)

**See also**:
- @42-spacing-layout.mdc - Spacing and typography foundations
- @43-visual-design.mdc - Colors, surfaces, borders, iconography
- @44-implementation-tokens.mdc - Accessibility, tokens, checklists

---

## 1. Component Rules (Buttons, Inputs, Lists)

### 1.1 Buttons

**Primary Button**:
- **Height**: `48-52px` (use `SPACING[12]` = 48px or custom 50px)
- **Radius**: `12-14px` (use `BORDER_RADIUS.sm` = 10-12, or `BORDER_RADIUS.md` = 14)
- **Text**: Medium/Semibold
- **No gradients**
- **Press state**: Darken background slightly; no ripple chaos

**Secondary Button**:
- Same size as primary
- Neutral background or border
- Never more visually dominant than primary

**Icon Buttons**:
- **Touch target min**: `44×44px` (accessibility requirement)
- **Icon size**: `18-22px`
- **One icon style set only** (stroke weight consistent)

**Implementation**:
```typescript
// Primary button
<TouchableOpacity
  style={{
    height: 50,
    borderRadius: BORDER_RADIUS.md,
    backgroundColor: theme.interactive.primary,
    paddingHorizontal: SPACING[6],
    justifyContent: 'center',
    alignItems: 'center',
  }}
  activeOpacity={0.8}
>
  <Text style={[TEXT_STYLES.button, { color: theme.text.inverse }]}>
    {title}
  </Text>
</TouchableOpacity>

// Icon button
<TouchableOpacity
  style={{
    width: 44,
    height: 44,
    justifyContent: 'center',
    alignItems: 'center',
  }}
>
  <Icon size={20} color={theme.text.primary} />
</TouchableOpacity>
```

---

### 1.2 Inputs

**Input Specifications**:
- **Height**: `48-52px` (match button height)
- **Label above input** (not inside) for premium clarity
- **Border**: `1px` subtle (use `StyleSheet.hairlineWidth` or `1`)
- **Focus**: Blue focus ring or border (no neon glow)

**Implementation**:
```typescript
<View>
  <Text style={[TEXT_STYLES.label, { marginBottom: SPACING[1] }]}>
    {label}
  </Text>
  <TextInput
    style={{
      height: 50,
      borderWidth: 1,
      borderColor: theme.border.default,
      borderRadius: BORDER_RADIUS.sm,
      paddingHorizontal: SPACING[4],
      ...TEXT_STYLES.body,
    }}
    onFocus={(e) => {
      e.target.setNativeProps({ borderColor: theme.interactive.primary });
    }}
  />
</View>
```

**❌ FORBIDDEN**: Labels inside inputs (floating labels are acceptable but not preferred for premium feel).

---

### 1.3 Lists

**List Specifications**:
- **Row height**: `56-64px` (consistent)
- **Dividers**: Hairline (`StyleSheet.hairlineWidth` or `1`)
- **Layout**: Left = label; Right = value/chevron/status
- **Avoid**: "Busy" rows with 5+ elements

**Implementation**:
```typescript
<View style={{
  height: 60,
  flexDirection: 'row',
  alignItems: 'center',
  justifyContent: 'space-between',
  paddingHorizontal: SPACING[4],
  borderBottomWidth: StyleSheet.hairlineWidth,
  borderBottomColor: theme.border.default,
}}>
  <Text style={TEXT_STYLES.body}>{label}</Text>
  <View style={{ flexDirection: 'row', alignItems: 'center', gap: SPACING[2] }}>
    <Text style={TEXT_STYLES.bodyEmphasis}>{value}</Text>
    <Icon name="chevron-right" size={20} />
  </View>
</View>
```

