## Quick Reference

### Button Specifications
- **Height**: 48-52px
- **Radius**: 10-14px
- **Touch target**: Min 44×44px (icons)
- **States**: Subtle darken on press

### Input Specifications
- **Height**: 48-52px (match buttons)
- **Labels**: Above input (not inside)
- **Borders**: 1px hairline
- **Focus**: Blue border (no glow)

### List Specifications
- **Row height**: 56-64px
- **Dividers**: Hairline
- **Layout**: Label left, value/chevron right

### Motion
- **Duration**: 150-220ms
- **Easing**: Ease-out
- **Avoid**: Bouncy springs, excessive spinners
- **Prefer**: Skeletons for loading states

### Content
- **Fewer labels**: Minimize UI noise
- **Shorter copy**: Concise text
- **Numbers**: Tabular numerals, aligned decimals
- **CTAs**: 1-2 max per screen

